Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:05.23,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Mulai hari ini kita akan memulai persiapan untuk tokudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:07.49,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Apa kalian sudah siap?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:08.23,Utama,ALL,0,0,0,,Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:11.42,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Tunjukkan kemampuan kita kepada biksu bejat itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:12.42,Utama,BOTH,0,0,0,,Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.98,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Aku punya pertanyaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:17.12,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Kalian pakai cawet warna apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:24.00,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Warna putih atau yang lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:27.14,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kiki-san, waktunya pendek, tolong serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:28.34,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Aku sungguh-sungguh serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:34.05,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Latihan adalah bertujuan mengembalikan jiwa dan raga\Nke kondisi yang murni.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:38.63,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Bahkan pakaian dalam sekalipun\Nharus sesuai ketentuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:41.68,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Yaitu harus warna putih polos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:45.25,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Aku tidak punya cawet warna putih,\Ntapi aku biasa pakai bokser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:47.24,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Punyaku lagi dicuci.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:49.19,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Aku hanya punya merah dan hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.91,Utama,BOTH,0,0,0,,Merah dan hitam?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:54.70,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Eh? Ko-Kok kalian kaget banget?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.41,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Enggak ada yang punya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:00:59.66,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:03.45,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Kalian akan berlatih tanpa mengenakan \Npakaian dalam hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:43.14,Utama,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,{\fn bd cartoon shout\fs20\c&HB943A0&\3c&HB5E1F9&\fade(200,400)\pos(688.79,387.625)}Episode 7:\NCawetmu warna apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.51,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,{\an1}Rasanya risih banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:45.50,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,{\an1}Apa kamu enggak terganggu\N ngelakuin hal sehina ini, Yuzuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:51.61,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Ya-Yah, aku malu, sih, anggap saja ini\N bagian dari latihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:57.82,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kiki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.33,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\pos(753.922,393.333)}Makasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.33,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\pos(557.769,396.333)}Aku benci.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:01.45,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Ucapanmu terdengar unik, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.95,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Pertama-tama kita mulai dari meditasi zazen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:08.86,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Tegakkan postur dan tenangkan pikiran kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:14.84,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Pikiran buruk apapun yang terbesit,\N jangan pernah terpengaruh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:19.34,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Siapapun yang gagal akan kupukul dengan kyosaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.34,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fn hey fun\b1\c&H020201&\3c&HFDFEFE&\pos(700.547,113.333)}Kyosaku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:28.35,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Terima kasih. Inilah latihan yang\N sudah lama kuinginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.59,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Menutup mulut, membuka sedikit mata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:37.05,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lalu bernapas perlahan-lahan melalui hidung.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.29,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inilah meditasi zazen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:56.38,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tidak memikirkan nafsu duniawi, \Naku hanya menghirup udara segar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:01.10,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kuyakin inilah yang dimaksud pikiran jernih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:28.37,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Ada apa, Akagami?\NBangun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.12,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Berikutnya menyalin sutera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.46,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Tulislah setiap aksaranya dengan teliti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:40.63,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aku ceroboh tadi, tapi kali ini pasti aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.88,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Wah, bagus juga, Akagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.42,AKEMITSU,AKAGMI,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya aku pernah magang\N mengajar kelas kaligrafi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.85,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Tulisan bagus dapat menjadi\N nilai tambah untuk jadi biksu kepala.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:56.82,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Kamu ajari juga Yuzuki, \Naku akan pergi sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.41,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-san, caramu memegang kuas ....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.16,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Seksi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.41,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Seksi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.62,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Ah, maaf! Jempolmu--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.50,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Aduh, nih, tisu--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.00,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H030604&\3c&HF6F8F8&\pos(525.722,53.605)}Selangkangan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.00,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H030604&\3c&HF6F8F8&\pos(224.762,415.76)}Tak pakai cangcut
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.88,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Bi-Biar kulap, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.13,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Mia-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.81,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Tenang saja, tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.14,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Berhenti, Mia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.06,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kenapa cuma aku yang kena?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.53,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Anu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.11,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Kami selalu menghalangimu hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.73,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kami harus meminta maaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.54,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Enggak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:06:00.70,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Tapi mungkin lebih baik kalian berdua enggak perlu memaksa ikut menemaniku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.80,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.88,Utama,BOTH,0,0,0,,Kami juga sudah beli cawet warna putih!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.05,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,BH juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.44,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Persiapan sudah sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:11.81,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bagus, Akagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.22,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.26,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mereka berdua memang terlihat mirip, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:18.92,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, ayo kita istirahat supaya punya tenaga untuk latihan besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.31,Utama,BOTH,0,0,0,,Siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.37,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kami pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.82,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Mulai hari ini, kalian bertiga tidur di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:32.45,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Selama masa latihan, setiap orang akan tidur\N di atas tikar tatami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:35.23,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Enggak ada salahnya membiasakan diri dari sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.02,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Mana bisa tidur di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.93,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Apalagi cuma pakai futon doang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:42.96,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Biasanya cewek dan cowok dipisah, 'kan, Kiki-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.40,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Eh? Kiki-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:45.96,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Ini dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.88,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Aku bisa tidur kalau begini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.02,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Itu dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.57,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Kamu cerdik, Akagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.60,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Apa yang kamu inginkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:02.45,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Untuk apa kamu memaksa dia\N buru-buru menjalani tokudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:08.11,Utama,HOAN,0,0,0,,Tiga bulan lagi, akan ada rapat dewan di kuil ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.66,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H070103&\3c&H40FF8B&\pos(92.492,31.091)}Rapat Dewan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:11.42,Utama,HOAN,0,0,0,,Ini keputusan para petinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.11,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H070103&\3c&H40FF8B&\move(92.492,31.091,736.524,27.196)}Rapat Dewan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:12.74,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.12,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H070103&\3c&H40FF8B&\pos(736.524,27.196)}Rapat Dewan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:19.69,Utama,HOAN,0,0,0,,Tolong jangan buat pertunanganku sia-sia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.38,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Ampun, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:31.02,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Terpaksa dengan cara paksa, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.89,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fn hey fun\pos(306.232,181.988)\c&H5F6058&\3c&H29251B&\frx16\fry30\frz326.8}Kuil Mikazuki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:41.19,Utama,BOTH,0,0,0,,Enggak bisa tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:48.37,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Aku ingin kalian melakukan latihan\N yang unik hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:57.81,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Ini juga termasuk hadiah atas usaha kalian selama ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.27,Utama,BOTH,0,0,0,,Hadiah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:09.05,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\c&H1C5F8A&\3c&H4EB4E4&\fnTimes New Roman\fs40\fay-.07\b1\pos(461.504,65.581)}Sauna
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:07.43,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kenapa di sauna?\NApalagi kenapa bisa campur begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.05,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Kamu enggak senang?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.03,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Justru aku senang makanya bingung ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.92,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Ini semacam cara paksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.80,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Kalian harus hadapi pikiran jorok ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:20.81,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,{\pos(366.953,452.333)}... dan perkuat kesabaran\N kalian menghadapi lawan jenis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.98,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Dan untuk merncapainya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:26.61,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Jalani aja, deh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.56,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Jalani apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.82,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Ayo berjuang, Akagami-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:34.21,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\pos(300.234,465.667)}Kalau segini saja ngeluh, kita \Nenggak mungkin sanggup mengejar\N tokudo dalam tiga bulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:37.07,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kau benar, Yuzuki--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.45,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aku baik-baik saja, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.95,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aku juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.89,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otakku penuh pikiran jorok!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:03.37,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apa latihan ini dapat membantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.85,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Te-Tempatnya agak sempit, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.93,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Ma-Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.61,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,A-Akagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:20.01,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Maaf, Mia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.62,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,A-Aku baik-baik saja, kok, Akagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:27.12,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Tapi aku ingin lampunya dimatikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.10,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Otakmu sudah tak waras!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.33,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Jangan begitu, Mia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:38.51,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Benar juga. Kita enggak boleh \Nmengganggu Yuzuki-san lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:43.06,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,A-Ayo kita bertukar cerita,\Nmisalnya hasil latihan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.64,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,I-Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.16,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kemarin kita berlatih menyalin sutera\N dan meditasi zazen, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:52.26,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Tidur bareng juga termasuk latihan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:53.65,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Oh ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:57.16,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,aku tahu satu hal setelah kita tidur bareng kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.16,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:01.28,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Aku punya fetish jakun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.86,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Jakun besarmu sangat menggoda, Akagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:08.79,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Itu bukan pencerahan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.37,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Lagi-lagi aku ngelantur?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:16.45,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Ba-Bagaimana denganmu, Akagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.55,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Be-Benar juga, kemarin malam ....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.60,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Aku mengeras semalaman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.56,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Jantan banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:28.19,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Apa yang aku katakan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:30.69,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-san merah banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.85,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenapa cuma ada pikiran jorok?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:41.88,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kalau begini, Yuzuki-san akan membenciku \Ndan tak layak menjalani tokudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:42.82,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.14,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:48.21,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Aku sudah mengerti tujuan Kiki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:53.71,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\pos(190.816,436.333)}Dia ingin kita merasakan makyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.67,Utama,BOTH,0,0,0,,Makyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.17,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fn hey fun\b1\c&H5D3478&\3c&H955AAA&\pos(424.124,103.425)\fade(300,500)}Makyo (Alam Setan)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:00.06,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Akhirnya Yuzuki-san konslet kepanasan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.97,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Apa karena aku mengganggunya terus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:06.47,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Bukan alam seperti itu!\NMakyo itu istilah dalam buddha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.77,Utama,PRIEST,0,0,0,,Akulah satu-satunya penghuni langit dan bumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.78,Utama,PRIEST,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aku lapar, pengen direbutin cewek!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:20.30,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Makyo adalah membiarkan diri dalam kondisi ekstrem supaya pikiran jorok dan nafsu duniawi keluar dari hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.66,Utama,PRIEST,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aku ingin tidur, pengen santai-santai ....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:29.75,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Dan setelah berhasil melewatinya,\N kita akan kebal terhadap pikiran jorok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.45,Utama,PRIEST,0,0,0,,{\an8}Pencerahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:34.75,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Walah, rupanya ini yang dimaksud Kiki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.37,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Iya, mungkin, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:39.37,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Berikutnya giliranmu, Yuzuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.01,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:44.39,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Nah, keluarkan semua ucapan seksimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.01,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Jangan disamain dengan \Nngomongin hal-hal jorok, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.27,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Ayo, ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:53.77,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,E-Etto ... aku ....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.33,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Ayo, ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:57.82,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enggak bisa kuceritain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:01.20,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kalau tubuh telanjang Akagami ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.20,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}... atau tubuh bawah Akagami-kun\N membuatku penasaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:09.04,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aku terus terngiang-ngiang tubuh telanjang dan hal-hal lain yang kulihat di hotel cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:14.66,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apalagi aku sempat memikirkan kelanjutannya,\Nenggak bisa aku ceritakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.06,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Selain itu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:24.80,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kayaknya aku enggak punya pikiran jorok, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:25.94,Utama,BOTH,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:28.94,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kau sudah menaklukan makyo \Ndan memasuki kondisi pikiran tanpa ego?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:31.08,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Kamu hebat, Yuzuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.56,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,I-Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.12,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Latihannya sudah selesai dan berhasil, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.66,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Ayo kasih tahu Kiki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:43.57,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aku enggak bisa ceritain, karena ini ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.98,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}... masalahku yang enggak \Nada hubungannya sama latihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:52.33,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Masa aku bilang hatiku gelisah\N melihat mereka berdua dekat ....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.13,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Pikiran kita sudah bebas dari ego, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.33,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\an8}Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.58,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enggak bisa kubilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:01.96,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Kalian sudah menyelesaikan latihan khususnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.93,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Kelihatannya efektif, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:04.72,Utama,ALL,0,0,0,,Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:07.97,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Aku merasa dapat mengendalikan\N semua pikiran jorokku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.27,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Iya, bagus sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:14.29,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Walau kalian meraih pencerahan,\Ntapi pikiran jorok akan tetap ada,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:18.10,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,makanya kalian perlu benar-benar menghadapinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:19.86,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:25.02,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Yah, jika hari ini ada yang mengaku \Nenggak punya pikiran jorok ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:29.38,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,... bisa dipastikan dia adalah\N orang paling mesum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:39.00,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Aku enggak mesum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:43.00,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,1)\fnhey fun\c&H2E353C&\3c&HBFE5FC&\b1\pos(560.438,69.333)}Semakin bijak, kian merunduk
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.89,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Kalian lumayan berkembang, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.02,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.97,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Siang nanti kalian beristirahat saja, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:06.44,Utama,YUZUKI/AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:07.68,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kenapa, Kiki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.60,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.42,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Bukannya latihannya baru saja dimulai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:15.82,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Tenanglah. Memaksakan diri hanya akan\N menyiksa tubuh kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:16.79,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Tapi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:19.37,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,"Merehatkan harta dan tahta."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.18,KIKI,KIKI,0,0,0,,Kamu mengerti, 'kan, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:35.31,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9F7F6&\3c&H63909B&\b1\pos(447.128,331.449)\fade(500,1)}Merehatkan harta dan tahta
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.94,Utama,BOTH,0,0,0,,Eh? Harta dan tahta?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:32.29,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,"Merehatkan harta dan tahta" berarti berhenti memikirkan kekayaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:35.31,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,lalu fokus kepada diri sendiri dan\N yang ada di sekitarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:39.19,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Itu syarat ketiga untuk meraih pencerahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:42.81,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Artinya, latihan kita juga perlu istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:46.20,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Aku mau main bareng Kagura lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:48.83,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tidak mungkin ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.69,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Masa hari ini libur?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:55.78,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Ada apa, Akagami-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.55,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Hari ini tanggal 24 Desember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:01.46,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Artinya, malam Natal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.46,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Eh? Kamu enggak suka Natal, Akagami-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:12.14,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Setiap Natal, Ayahku selalu ribut dengan\N semua kekasihnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:17.45,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Dan selalu ada pertumpahan darah di rumahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:23.90,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Natal serem.\NNatal menyiksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.48,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Etto ....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.43,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, Akagami-kun ....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.49,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Mau pergi berdua denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.98,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kita mengadakan pesta Natal bersama besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.50,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Eh? Meski di kuil?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:48.13,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Iya. Lalu kita juga akan saling bertukar hadiah,\Nayo kita pilih bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.50,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Ba-Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.64,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kamu kenapa, Akagami-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:57.64,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bepergian berdua di malam Natal \Nmaknanya terlalu dahsyat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.02,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ditambah bareng Yuzuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.25,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lagu-lagu Natal dan hiasan lampu di mana-mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:08.78,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seluruh kota dipenuhi suasana gembira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.86,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Malam Natal sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:14.78,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tapi aku pantang menyerah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.16,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Ayo pergi, Akagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.66,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:20.58,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.00,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.84,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Imutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.68,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Terlalu keasikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:42.93,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jadi, ini sihir Malam Natal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.85,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aku masih butuh latihan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.45,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kamu sudah milih hadiahmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.44,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Eh? Belum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:52.26,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Aku bingung mau beli apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:56.02,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Enggak usah dipikir susah-susah, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.45,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:02.70,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Beli saja hadiah yang kamu inginkan sebagai bentuk terima kasih kepada semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.72,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:09.65,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Oh ya, aku tahu toko bagus untukmu, Akagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.71,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnhey fun\fs20\c&H4E9FA7&\frz350.2\frx348\fry2\3c&H49393A&\move(451.79,105.616,450.207,87.175)}Toko Perlengkapan Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.71,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnhey fun\fs20\c&H4E9FA7&\frz350.2\frx348\fry2\3c&H483D3A&\move(436.493,195.188,436.493,188.865)}~Tsukishita~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.72,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fn hey fun\frz347.1\pos(491.881,87.175)\c&H59ADC0&\3c&H3E2E35&}Toko Perlengkapan Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.72,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(462.341,399.095)\fnhey fun\frz354\c&H45A2B9&\3c&H2C252E&}~Tsukishita~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.72,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Toko Perlengkapan Buddha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:19.22,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Benar. Ini toko milik seniorku di sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.68,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Barang-barang di sini\Nmerupakan kebutuhan kuil,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:24.34,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,jadi mungkin kamu akan mudah memilihnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:26.98,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.62,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Tasbih, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:32.84,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kamu mau itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.83,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,TIdak, aku tidak punya soalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:39.62,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Oh, aku juga cuma punya tasbih kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.62,YUZUKI,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Tasbih kecil?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:44.14,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Ada tasbih formal dan kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:46.00,Utama,SIGN RIGHT,0,0,0,,{\fn\c&H01F8FF&\3c&HC1B048&\fade(350,1)\pos(625.335,103.669)}Tasbih {\c&HFFFCFE&}Kecil
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:46.00,Utama,SIGN RIGHT,0,0,0,,{\c&HC2B140&\3c&HFFFFF9&\fade(350,1)\frz354.4\pos(701.91,354.03)}Jumlah\Nstandar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:46.00,Utama,SIGN LEFT,0,0,0,,{\fn\c&H01F8FF&\3c&H1914EE&\fade(350,1)\pos(248.194,102.667)}Tasbih{\c&HFFFFFF&} Formal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:46.00,Utama,SIGN LEFT,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,1)\c&H953FC6&\3c&HEFFFFF&\frz10.65\pos(108.954,450.708)}Tasbih Formal\NJumlahnya\N108!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:49.10,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Tasbih formal dipakai untuk acara-acara penting seperti ritual tokudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:54.45,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Tapi harganya lumayan mahal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:58.53,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kita harus meminjam punya Kiki-san atau keluargaku untuk ritual tokudo nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.76,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:04.52,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Aku ingin segera jadi biksu dan beli tasbih sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:09.32,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Jangan tunda-tunda terus,\Nbeli saja sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.29,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Mari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.02,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Selamat datang, Yuzukin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.21,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Lama enggak ketemu.\NDia adalah Akagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.30,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.54,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Dia seniorku, Mari-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:19.53,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Halo, halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:23.03,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Kalau lagi cari tasbih, aku punya yang bagus, nih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.86,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Tasbih sepasang kekasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:28.29,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Eh? Ada model begitu juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:34.90,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Ada, soalnya dalam pernikahan Buddhis, \Npasangan saling bertukar tasbih, bukan cincin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.12,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Bertukar tasbih?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.55,AKEMITSU,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Rupanya enggak banyak yang tahu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:44.29,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Ada juga untuk kekasih dan pasutri yang ingin subur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:47.24,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kenapa nawarinnya yang begitu doang, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:49.16,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua kekasih, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:49.88,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Kekas--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:52.78,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Enggak, bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:53.82,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:56.82,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Habisnya kalian berdua pergi bareng pas malam Natal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:59.20,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Kukira kalian lagi kencan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.21,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eh? Dia baru menyadarinya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:13.59,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Anu, sumpah kami bukan kekasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.41,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Beneran?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:17.72,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Sama sekali bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.30,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,I-Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.80,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Tapi wajah Yuzukin memerah, jadi kurang yakin, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:23.60,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.47,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Jangan lihat aku, Akagami-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.73,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Yuzukin semangat banget, tuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.35,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Biasanya dia pakai baju yang lebih kasual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.11,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Dia juga berdandan hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:40.36,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Selain itu, dia juga sangat senang sampai gendu--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.36,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Mari-san, aku beli ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.09,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Makasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:46.66,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Sumpah bukan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.62,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\c&H733BC5&\3c&HFCFEFE&\fs20\frx358\fry346\frz336.6\move(288.225,18.667,312.244,116)}Silakan gabung!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.62,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\c&H733BC5&\3c&HDBDBEB&\fs20\frz-25\fax.1\move(314.913,201.333,336.263,302.667)}Pengalaman membuat tasbih!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.62,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\c&H474852&\3c&HDBEAF3&\frz-27\fax.1\fs20\move(380.581,259.996,404.318,361.16)}1.000 yen~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.62,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\c&H474852&\3c&HDBEAF3&\fs20\frz-30\fax.2\move(289.559,289.333,314.913,389.333)}Usia 5 tahun ke atas
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:47.50,Utama,MARI,0,0,0,,Iya, iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.75,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Kamu sudah milih hadiahnya, Akagami-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.00,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Iya, berkat bantuanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:00.88,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:07.67,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apa Yuzuki-san mencoba menghiburku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.50,AKEMITSU,AKAGAMI,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-san, tidak sabar untuk besok, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.21,YUZUKI,YUZUKI,0,0,0,,Iya, Akagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:24.15,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,Sudah Natal sekarang, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:26.49,KURAGE,KURAGE,0,0,0,,Tahun ini berlalu begitu cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:30.28,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,Bukankah belakangan ini jadi sibuk banget, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:36.13,KURAGE,KURAGE,0,0,0,,Benar, perubahannya drastis banget,\Nsampai-sampai aku menjadi wanita dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.66,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,Yang sudah pasti berubah itu Mia, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:42.26,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Hasil latihanku sudah terlihat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.38,Utama,BOTH,0,0,0,,Malah tambah seksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.76,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:47.94,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,Awalnya kamu terlihat polos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:50.89,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnhey fun\c&H2544DF&\3c&H000212&\bord1.333\fade(1000,1)\frz5.853\pos(617.547,155.416)}Umbar aurat?\NDasar biadab!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.55,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kebiri saja dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:50.89,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnhey fun\c&H2544DF&\3c&H000000&\bord1.333\fs34\fade(1000,1)\frz13.29\pos(163.645,215.467)}Tebus penghinaanmu \Ndengan nyawamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:50.89,KURAGE,KURAGE,0,0,0,,Tapi sekarang udah buka-bukaan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.30,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,Gaya pakaianmu juga berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.90,KURAGE,KURAGE,0,0,0,,Lekuk tubuhmu makin terlihat jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.06,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Aku enggak bermaksud begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.15,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,Maaf, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:03.65,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,Kamu terlihat cocok, jelas bukan karena alasan yang enggak senonoh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:07.33,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Aku hanya ingin memamerkan nenenku pada Akagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.78,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,Enggak senonoh banget!{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:11.04,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Bukan 'gitu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.62,KURAGE,KURAGE,0,0,0,,Kamu juga makin mesum, Mbak Tsukuyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:15.29,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,Enggak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.79,KURAGE,KURAGE,0,0,0,,Mbak Yuzuki jelas mesum akut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:30.04,KAGURA,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Wah, wah, berarti pria itu telah mengubah kita semua, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:36.44,KAGURA,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Padahal kita berempat dulu sempat berencana untuk mengusir Akagami-san, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.03,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:42.85,KURAGE,KURAGE,0,0,0,,Kuyakin perubahan paling besar\N adalah kedatangan Akagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:47.45,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,Sekarang enggak ada lagi\N yang ingin mengusirnya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:48.73,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:01.37,KAGURA,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Akagami-san orang yang menarik, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:08.05,KAGURA,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Benar-benar mengganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:10.87,KAGURA,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Aku harus mengusirnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:49.92,KAGURA,KAGURA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Pertanyaan: Bagian tubuh apa yang gondal-gandul?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:24:00.04,Utama,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fn bd cartoon shout\blur1.333\pos(441.171,323.569)}Selanjutnya\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NMelihat Kura-Kura Menandakan Keberuntungan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.41,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bagian yang suka kembang-kempis, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:53.49,TSUKUYO,TSUKUYO,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hei, Mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:56.86,MIA,MIA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dan jika sudah memainkan bagian itu sendiri,\Ntandanya sudah dewasa, ya.
